[GO Into Your Heart]

17
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:33,010
[Episode 38]

18
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:38,330
Today, at the China-Korea Invitational GO Tournament, in the game between Xie Hanzhou 9th dan and Sheng Jingchu 9th dan,

19
00:01:38,330 --> 00:01:42,450
the high-profile battle between master and disciple came to an end.

20
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:46,210
In the end, after having tied for the first two games with the score of 1:1,

21
00:01:46,210 --> 00:01:49,290
Sheng Jingchu won the final round and became the champion.

22
00:01:49,290 --> 00:01:51,200
Look, Master.

23
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,140
Even if it's aggressive to put it in this corner,

24
00:01:55,140 --> 00:01:57,170
it's still too risky.

25
00:01:57,170 --> 00:02:00,260
If you let the black stone come out here,

26
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:03,370
it can cause unnecessary conflict.

27
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:05,690
Unlike this large knight move.

28
00:02:06,710 --> 00:02:09,100
It blocks off this point

29
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:11,150
and covers a large area here.

30
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:13,710
One of the two is guaranteed, from the left and to the right.

31
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,850
Plus...

32
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:19,310
the advantage accumulated from the first half, it's a smooth transition.

33
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:22,110
This way, it's a guaranteed win.

34
00:02:23,490 --> 00:02:25,630
Well done.

35
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:30,500
Why didn't I think of this reverse strategy?

36
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:35,430
Jingchu, your GO skills have improved a lot.

37
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,640
Also, it's more comprehensive now.

38
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:41,030
Look, no matter if it's a majestic, imposing move,

39
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:43,780
or a balanced, skillful play,

40
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:47,560
you can handle them all.

41
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,850
Thank you for your praise, Master.

42
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:56,780
I've never seen someone this happy doing the post-game analysis after losing.

43
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:59,720
It means that compared to some titles of champion,

44
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:02,790
he loves his beloved disciple more.

45
00:03:02,790 --> 00:03:04,530
Don't say that.

46
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:06,440
It's not that Master prefers one over another.

47
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:10,970
I believe if I won, Master would be just as happy.

48
00:03:10,970 --> 00:03:12,770
- Of course.
- Right?

49
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:15,500
The question is, can you beat him?

50
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:18,120
Senior Brother, what you just said sounds so—

51
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:20,370
There's still logic to what he said.

52
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:26,700
That's right. That's right. I thought the same, too.

53
00:03:27,890 --> 00:03:31,420
Lan Lan, do you think Senior Brother Jing and Master

54
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:34,240
won't end any time soon, right?

55
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:46,330
What do you mean?

56
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:48,700
I have to treat you two to lunch again, is that it?

57
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,760
Someone who's always losing at GO?

58
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:53,760
You're a second-generation GO player.

59
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:58,130
You're not wrong.

60
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:00,710
- Let's go?
- Yay!

61
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:04,320
This way we can bring some takeout back for Senior Brother Jing and Master.

62
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:07,590
Let's not pack takeout for them. They're already winners. Do they need to takeout?

63
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:09,660
That's right.

64
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:12,340
- How did the fans find us here?
- They're coming out!

65
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:14,480
Hurry! Hurry!

66
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,120
Let's take separate routes.

67
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,770
You're the romantic GO player!

68
00:04:18,770 --> 00:04:20,730
The Taste of Memories made us cry so hard!

69
00:04:20,730 --> 00:04:24,030
I didn't know romantic men like you existed in real life!

70
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:25,890
- What do you mean?
- Autograph, please!

71
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:29,520
Please, sign it!

72
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:33,030
They turned out to be Senior Brother's fans!

73
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:35,760
I had thought he was going to die alone.

74
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:42,130
It looks like he can give love a go again in this stage of life.

75
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:49,300
Seeing Eldest Senior Brother this famous, do you feel a sense of loss?

76
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,900
No need to rush. No need to rush.

77
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:56,550
Wanting to be famous was a childish wish I had for years.

78
00:04:56,550 --> 00:04:58,720
Now that I have you, you're enough for me.

79
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,880
That's some survival instinct you got.

80
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,870
But I like it.

81
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:06,460
- Let's go.
- Please sign this for me!
- Eldest Senior Brother!

82
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:09,150
We'll wait for you at the bridge.

83
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:10,820
[Jiuzhou Hall]

84
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:30,850
Master, you've got the championship in hand now.

85
00:05:30,850 --> 00:05:34,170
And I'm finally a professional GO player.

86
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:45,190
You're only a first dan. Is this necessary?

87
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:48,260
Master, why don't you understand my effort?

88
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,860
As Sheng Jingchu's only student,

89
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:52,610
this one dan is very meaningful.

90
00:05:52,610 --> 00:05:56,620
- Therefore, I'm giving it to you as a gift.
- Oh.

91
00:05:57,470 --> 00:06:01,170
As Sheng Jingchu's only student,

92
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:04,380
you might be stuck in first dan.

93
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:06,490
Why are you cursing me?

94
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:09,750
I was teasing you. How could that happen?

95
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:12,460
Turns out Master still has confidence in me.

96
00:06:12,460 --> 00:06:14,300
You misunderstood.

97
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,780
I'm confident in myself.

98
00:06:19,410 --> 00:06:23,670
Then, Master, could you share some of your confidence with me?

99
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:28,120
- For what?
- After receiving the award, I have something really important to do,

100
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:32,560
which requires enough confidence and courage. In fact, the more the better.

101
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:36,820
Have you read the GO book I gave you?

102
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,620
Lay it out.

103
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:55,150
[National Amateur GO Championship]

104
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:20,470
[6-inch Vanilla Chiffon Cake]

105
00:07:22,690 --> 00:07:25,170
Why are you still up?

106
00:07:34,530 --> 00:07:36,810
What are you thinking about?

107
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,540
What's wrong?

108
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:45,830
Why didn't I get a text?

109
00:07:48,820 --> 00:07:50,530
What?

110
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:53,040
Jiang Yuda won the National Amateur GO Championship.

111
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,080
But he didn't tell me anything.

112
00:07:55,080 --> 00:08:00,020
It-It's fine if he doesn't have the time to call me, but at least send a text, right?

113
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:02,500
And I encouraged him and supported him so much before.

114
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:04,620
So ungrateful.

115
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:08,190
Why do you care about Jiang Yuda so much all of a sudden?

116
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:10,790
Have you started to like him?

117
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:19,810
Have I?

118
00:08:19,810 --> 00:08:21,740
Who are you asking?

119
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:27,410
Sis, I've never seen you so preoccupied before.

120
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:32,340
You're like a little girl in love.

121
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:37,690
People do this... when they are in love?

122
00:08:37,690 --> 00:08:39,500
What?

123
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:42,360
Are you asking the more experienced one to teach you?

124
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,190
Cheng Zhiliao, you better be careful I don't... ka ka ka!

125
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:47,250
Don't ka me.

126
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:50,690
You can ka me as much as you want.

127
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:56,730
But sometimes, a true opportunity for love only comes around once.

128
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:59,150
Did you really think it through?

129
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,440
I think so.

130
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:09,930
In the past, I set so many harsh conditions.

131
00:09:09,930 --> 00:09:13,960
I always kept thinking I had to find a particular kind of person.

132
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:18,400
After that, I was longing for a soulmate.

133
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:21,380
Now I think Jiang Yuda was right.

134
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:23,620
I overthought it.

135
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:28,020
Love should be simple. As long as I'm happy, that's enough.

136
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,900
What about Brother Xu Chi?

137
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:33,530
Are you really not going to consider him?

138
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:37,020
I've never thought about accepting him from the beginning.

139
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:40,980
What's more, I don't want to give him any hope or mislead him.

140
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:45,700
But Brother Xu Chi has been very persistent with you.

141
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:50,690
Do you know that in this world,

142
00:09:50,690 --> 00:09:54,810
the hardest thing to change is someone's mind.

143
00:09:54,810 --> 00:09:56,870
Think about it, Zhiliao.

144
00:09:56,870 --> 00:10:00,620
If I reluctantly agreed to be with him because of his persistence,

145
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:03,430
then I'd suffer every day after that.

146
00:10:03,430 --> 00:10:06,830
He'd definitely be able to tell that I wasn't happy.

147
00:10:06,830 --> 00:10:09,630
How is that a happy ending?

148
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:13,600
Instead, there'll be two more unhappy people on earth.

149
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:19,620
But do you really think that you and Jiang Yuda are the right fit?

150
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:22,540
What's the right fit?

151
00:10:24,050 --> 00:10:26,680
How does one measure it?

152
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:30,060
I don't know.

153
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:34,240
The only thing I know is that when I'm with him,

154
00:10:35,070 --> 00:10:37,170
I'm very happy.

155
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:49,120
It looks like you're ready.

156
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,500
What's there to get ready for?

157
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:54,310
If he dares confess, then I'll dare to accept it.

158
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:02,770
Why are you staring at me?

159
00:11:02,770 --> 00:11:04,730
Did I say something wrong?

160
00:11:04,730 --> 00:11:07,650
Shouldn't he confess first?!

161
00:11:07,650 --> 00:11:10,310
Or... Or should I say it first?

162
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:13,100
Sis, it looks like

163
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:16,300
when it comes to love, you've already been ka ka ka'ed.

164
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,770
Stop joking around!

165
00:11:18,770 --> 00:11:20,910
You don't... Who do you think he is?

166
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,970
I'm just mad.

167
00:11:22,970 --> 00:11:27,390
He won the championship and he didn't even tell me. I shouldn't have supported him and helped him so much.

168
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:29,250
Ungrateful. I don't have time to bother with him.

169
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:30,980
I'm going to go get my beauty sleep.

170
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:34,080
- Are you going to sleep and drink at the same time?
- I can't sleep.

171
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:44,090
[Pinecone Video]

172
00:11:57,350 --> 00:11:58,410
[Noodles]

173
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:12,670
Oh, I see. You're posting in your Moments, but you can't even give me a call?

174
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:19,380
Well done. If you're this talented then don't bother ever contacting me again in this lifetime!

175
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:22,070
Don't bother ever contacting me again in this lifetime!

176
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:31,710
Come in.

177
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:35,490
What's wrong? Who's made our anchorwoman Cheng angry?

178
00:12:35,490 --> 00:12:37,120
It's nothing.

179
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:40,710
What's wrong? Did you need anything from me?

180
00:12:40,710 --> 00:12:43,180
The outcome of the first episode of The Taste of Memories was exceptional.

181
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:47,490
There's food, there's emotion, there were tears, and plot twists.

182
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:50,950
But the key point is that the audience observed our production team's sincerity.

183
00:12:50,950 --> 00:12:54,030
That we're not the kind of show that racks our brain just to make something go viral.

184
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:58,760
Actually, our intention was to do our best to fulfill that person's dream.

185
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:03,330
Even though this time we didn't have a fairy tale ending,

186
00:13:03,330 --> 00:13:06,470
it was all thanks to Zhiliao, that at least they found a taste of their memories.

187
00:13:06,470 --> 00:13:09,000
That's right. President Wang also had similar thoughts.

188
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:13,690
Don't you think the two of you, beautiful Cheng sisters, one brings the heart, the other brings the stomach;

189
00:13:13,690 --> 00:13:15,530
the two together create amazing chemistry.

190
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:19,530
So I'm here today to discuss with you whether we could invite Zhiliao to be our Food Correspondent.

191
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:21,510
And formally work with the program department.

192
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:23,990
The filming location will be set at Uncle Cheng's Restaurant.

193
00:13:23,990 --> 00:13:26,340
I think it should be okay.

194
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:28,420
Let me go home and check with Zhiliao first.

195
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:30,430
I don't think it'll be a problem.

196
00:13:33,010 --> 00:13:35,410
[Jiang Yuda]

197
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:43,500
All right. You get back to work, I won't bother you.

198
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:44,970
Okay.

199
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:54,180
- Hello?
- Hello? Sister Cheng.

200
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:57,680
What's up? I'm busy.

201
00:13:57,680 --> 00:14:03,520
It'll only take a few minutes. I want to see you tonight. Is that okay?

202
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:05,700
- See each other?
- Yes.

203
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:08,230
What for?

204
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:11,040
I won the Amateur GO championship.

205
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:14,350
It's to recognize my success. Of course, I want to celebrate with my master, Cheng Liao,

206
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:18,250
Senior Sister Lan, Junior Uncle, Senior Uncle,

207
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:22,140
and you. All get together for a meal to celebrate.

208
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:26,140
So many people?

209
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:29,130
All right. I got it.

210
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:33,200
I'll send you the address later, just follow the GPS.

211
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,720
Okay.

212
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:48,340
Jiang Yuda, what kind of lousy address did you send me?

213
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:51,370
Why did you ask me to come to a bridge on such a cold night?!

214
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:55,230
You better hurry and show up. Do you hear me?

215
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:56,790
Hello?

216
00:14:57,550 --> 00:15:01,180
Jiang Yuda!

217
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:35,170
This is the place where we first met.

218
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,730
If you hadn't said anything, I wouldn't have realized it.

219
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:01,150
Cheng Yi.

220
00:16:02,490 --> 00:16:08,060
Maybe to you, this is just an ordinary pedestrian bridge.

221
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:12,620
But in my heart, it holds a lot of significance.

222
00:16:14,230 --> 00:16:17,460
That night, you pulled my clothing,

223
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:20,800
pulled me down from the railing and said to me,

224
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:24,360
"Please move. You're in the scene."

225
00:16:26,730 --> 00:16:31,070
From that moment on, I felt like a new chapter had started in my life.

226
00:16:31,070 --> 00:16:35,830
It was also from that day on, that aside from GO,

227
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:40,750
I had one more important life goal. That is...

228
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:46,140
I wanted to be with you.

229
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:19,880
I... just...

230
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:23,360
I-I know that right now, I may not have achieved

231
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:27,050
- the ideal boyfriend standard in your heart.
- I don't want any standards.

232
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:31,040
Forget all about those useless standards.

233
00:17:31,040 --> 00:17:35,030
- But didn't you used to say—
- Stop rambling and get to the point.

234
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:45,880
Since I've already entered your scene,

235
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:49,490
then I never want to leave.

236
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:52,610
Cheng Yi,

237
00:17:55,530 --> 00:17:57,690
let's be together.

238
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:15,890
Why weren't you this skilled last time?

239
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:17,980
Last time?

240
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:28,290
So do you prefer skilled or unskilled?

241
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:32,000
Doesn't matter.

242
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:41,740
♫ Little dreams are flying high ♫

243
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:53,960
♫ You're my most important treasure ♫

244
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:17,220
Vice President Xu, have you seen it? Cheng Yi is truly our number one news anchorwoman.

245
00:20:17,220 --> 00:20:20,470
She got us a big piece of news on New Year's Eve.

246
00:20:20,470 --> 00:20:23,010
It's already gone viral on the Internet.

247
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:27,410
I've already written a detailed explanation about it on my account the first chance I got.

248
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:30,030
This is Cheng Yi's private life!

249
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,330
Who gave you the right to spread it wildly?!

250
00:20:32,330 --> 00:20:36,580
