00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:21,190
I'm fine. Really.

510
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:25,070
If you really have that much free time,

511
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:27,210
go somewhere with me.

512
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:30,530
[Beloved Father and Mother]

513
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:36,000
Let me, Master.

514
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:39,220
Jingchu, I have a few things to say to your dad and mom.

515
00:36:39,220 --> 00:36:42,370
You two, go stand further over there, okay?

516
00:36:42,370 --> 00:36:44,540
- Okay.
- Go ahead.

517
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:51,440
[Beloved Father and Mother]

518
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:54,570
I haven't visited for a long time.

519
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:58,790
Tell you what,

520
00:36:58,790 --> 00:37:03,220
Jingchu is so happy right now.

521
00:37:06,390 --> 00:37:09,810
He met a smart,

522
00:37:09,810 --> 00:37:13,620
empathetic young lady.

523
00:37:14,250 --> 00:37:17,710
She cured his eyes!

524
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:21,070
Jingchu has so much promise.

525
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:25,150
He even defeated me this time in the competition.

526
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:28,660
I'm so proud of him.

527
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:31,850
All right.

528
00:37:31,850 --> 00:37:35,920
From now on, even if I can't be there for him,

529
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:39,630
he'll still be happy.

530
00:37:58,150 --> 00:38:00,610
Where am I?

531
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,540
Where..?

532
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:17,890
Master, what's wrong?

533
00:38:18,510 --> 00:38:22,130
Young lady, do you know me?

534
00:38:24,570 --> 00:38:26,360
Master,

535
00:38:27,310 --> 00:38:29,230
are you all right?

536
00:38:30,310 --> 00:38:32,910
Jingchu,

537
00:38:32,910 --> 00:38:35,890
my head is suddenly...

538
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:40,280
- suddenly dizzy...
- Master!

539
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:42,570
Master!

540
00:38:42,570 --> 00:38:45,130
- Master!
- Master!

541
00:38:57,670 --> 00:39:00,360
Panda, don't worry.

542
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:02,770
He'll definitely be okay.

543
00:39:04,580 --> 00:39:07,400
Jingchu! How is he?

544
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:09,290
How is he?

545
00:39:12,070 --> 00:39:16,090
The doctor said it's a complication caused by his hypertension.

546
00:39:16,090 --> 00:39:18,120
A ministroke.

547
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:21,800
That's why he temporarily lost his memory.

548
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,070
He's not in any danger right now.

549
00:39:24,070 --> 00:39:27,890
- But he needs to be hospitalized for further observation.
- Memory loss?

550
00:39:27,890 --> 00:39:29,920
Why won't he listen to our advice?

551
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:34,800
He just got discharged and everyone told him to rest and quit smoking and drinking. He just won't listen!

552
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:37,770
All right, Senior Brother. Don't panic.

553
00:39:37,770 --> 00:39:40,720
Master will be fine. We will take care of him together. Okay?

554
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:05,260
If I hadn't taken Master to the cemetery,

555
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:09,540
he wouldn't haven't been so exhausted.

556
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:12,240
Then he wouldn't have passed out, right?

557
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:23,130
Panda, don't blame yourself too much.

558
00:40:23,130 --> 00:40:26,510
The doctor said the light exercise was fine.

559
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:28,580
We couldn't have anticipated

560
00:40:28,580 --> 00:40:31,580
something like this is to happen.

561
00:40:32,870 --> 00:40:35,360
I really am scared.

562
00:40:40,980 --> 00:40:42,910
It's not your fault.

563
00:40:43,640 --> 00:40:45,840
It's really not your fault.

564
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:58,740
I've told you already that I'm fine.

565
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:01,160
Just let me go home.

566
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:03,480
If I keep lying in here,

567
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:06,570
