568
00:41:06,570 --> 00:41:09,380
Dad, can we stop doing this over and over?

569
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:11,810
Just behave and stay in the hospital for two days. What's wrong with that?

570
00:41:11,810 --> 00:41:14,230
