574
00:41:22,570 --> 00:41:26,390
You've always been so easily flustered since you were a kid.

575
00:41:26,390 --> 00:41:30,560
I've told you that I...

576
00:41:32,090 --> 00:41:35,140
What's wrong? Are you feeling all right, Dad?

577
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:39,300
Where was I?

578
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:42,170
